# AgToosa Ship Rules

When executing `/agtoosa-ship` or any shipping work, follow `Docs/AgToosa_Ship.md` precisely.

## Key constraints

- All pre-flight checks must pass before deployment begins (no 🔴 Critical findings, all Linear tickets closed).
- Zero-downtime deployment strategy is required — verify rollback plan exists before deploying.
- Archive the active spec to `Docs/archived/` with the completion date in the filename.
- Update `Docs/AgToosa_Changelog.md` and `Docs/Master-Plan.md` after a successful ship.
- Always end with a retro summary and a suggested next story.
